nodes.text: "The Gangsters of Galzez" is a comic strip written by Martin Fisher, drawn by Bob Molesworth and edited by Gunther Nickel. The story was published in the twentieth issue of the Star Wars Rebels Magazine series by Egmont UK Ltd, which was released on August 10, 2016.
According to Fisher, the story takes place between the Star Wars Rebels episodes "Shroud of Darkness" and "The Forgotten Droid."
